our journey into data really for the DCC. We started a few years ago

00:00:13.520 --> 00:00:19.120
and it's been a really interesting journey and we've enjoyed it all the way but firstly I'd

00:00:19.120 --> 00:00:25.280
like to say thank you to everyone for joining us. It's really great to be part of this community

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:30.799
we've had a lot of help along our way and it's nice to sort of give something back.

00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:36.880
On top of that I'd like to say thank you to our studios they've been a fantastic help all along

00:00:36.880 --> 00:00:43.040
and the journey couldn't have been done without them. My name's Oliver Bridges I'm head of data

00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:50.320
science at the DCC and I'm going to show you our journey from having a few canned reports

00:00:51.119 --> 00:00:59.119
